response.name: Git with HTTP
response.yaml:
connector:
  name: SampleGitConnector
  identifier: SampleGitConnectorId
  description: Sample Git Connector
  orgIdentifier: orgId
  projectIdentifier: projectId
  tags:
    - tag1_key : tag1_value
  type: Git
  spec:
    url: https://github.com/somegitaccount/somegitrepo.git
    branchName: master
    type: Http
    connectionType: ACCOUNT
    spec:
      username: abc@dummy.com
      passwordRef: somePasswordRef
    gitSync:
      enabled: false
      customCommitAttributes: someAttribute
      syncEnabled: false
